# Affiliate pipeline flow

Canonical design: **`docs/PIPELINE_SYSTEM_DESIGN.md`**  
Launch checklist: **`docs/LAUNCH_TODO.md`**

## End-to-end (one product)

```
scout → owner approves product → Module 4 image
  → product-video-prompt-builder → Kling 5s (KLING_MODE=std, audio off)
  → video-editor (pan loop ~10s) + video-caption-writer (pain hook, no sale/price words)
  → module1-qc-runner → PASS only
  → factory_cli enqueue --account affiliate_main
  → factory_cli post --account affiliate_main --confirm
```

## CLI reference

```bash
python3 -m shorts_bot.tiktok_shop.scout_cli run --preset middle_core --limit 15
python3 -m shorts_bot.tiktok_shop.factory_cli make-clip --product "NAME"
python3 -m shorts_bot.tiktok_shop.factory_cli qc --video PATH --product "NAME" --caption "..." --account affiliate_main
python3 -m shorts_bot.tiktok_shop.factory_cli enqueue --video PATH --product "NAME" --caption "..." --account affiliate_main
python3 -m shorts_bot.tiktok_shop.factory_cli post --account affiliate_main --confirm
python3 -m shorts_bot.tiktok_shop.factory_cli status
```

## Product research

- **FastMoss required** at launch — pick in app (path A) or API scout when wired
- FastMoss covers ad badges, trend, filters (Module 3) — no separate Kalodata
- Presets: `middle_core` (default), `two_hundred` when asked

## GOOD clip definition

- Module 1 QC **zero violations**
- Course pan loop + white box / black text caption (`VIDEO_EDITOR.md`)
- Module 7: **no** sale, price, discount, coupon, free shipping in caption
- Regen on fail — do not lower standards for speed

## Launch batch (8–10)

1. Sections E→G in `LAUNCH_TODO.md` before Launch Date eve
2. Queue 8–10 on `affiliate_main`
3. **12:00 AM** Launch Date: post #1 only → **7 calendar day clock starts**
4. Posts #2–10: every **≥30 minutes**
5. Week 1: repeat 8–10/day; track commission toward **$1k**

## Account config

- Purchased account: `affiliate_main` in `data/tiktok_shop/accounts.json`
- `post_via: zernio` · `enabled: true` after owner connects in Zernio dashboard
- Bubble four accounts are **separate track** — do not post affiliate clips to bubble IDs

## Long jobs

Kling, batch render, scout: run in **background**; poll every 1–2 min. Log to mission feed.
